snippet.title: Small Screen
snippet.description:
What is Small Screen? It’s pretty simple really. Small Screen is a place completely focused on delivering content on cinema, TV shows, video games and comics. In short, all things pop culture related.

Things that we love include all of Marvel's content (the MCU, their comics, everything they putting on Disney Plus), DC (the DCEU especially), and Star Wars (we are fans of the new Star Wars trilogy). We also love to chat about everything that comes to Netflix, Disney Plus, Amazon Prime Video and HBO Max... We love to stream stuff! We're also big James Bond fans here at Small Screen. I thought it would be good of us to mention some names of actors we love: Keanu Reeves, Michael Keaton and Johnny Depp.

#ReleaseTheSnyderCut #ReleaseTheAyerCut

This is the sort of stuff we like to talk about in our daily lives, so we thought, why not make videos about it?! We love pop culture and we hope that you’ll love our videos. 

So what are you waiting for? Jump in and join the community!
